data.description: Great opportunity to own a well maintained, second-level condo with convenient access to modern amenities and military bases! This 3 bed, 2 bath home highlights spectacular views of Pikes Peak and an abundance of natural lighting throughout. Kitchen has ample counter space and storage, pantry, and walk-out to balcony. Spacious owners suite with 5-piece bath and walk-in closet. Ring system included! Unit offers two parking spaces and two exterior storage closets.
